VERSION HISTORY
---------------
0.5.0 - 2012-08-30
cover all AKE state transitions

0.1.1 - 2012-08-10
TLV disconnect is supported

0.1.0 - 2012-07-30
DH key rotation added, basic functionality runs

0.0.9a - 2012-07-26
able to do AKE and secure chat but without DH key rotation
